# AGENTS.md — <!-- PARAMETERIZE: project_name -->

Master rules for this repo. Agent-agnostic. Applies to every coding session, in every tool. Claude Code reads this via `CLAUDE.md` (which imports this file). Codex reads it directly.

This file is intentionally short. Detailed rules live in `.claude/rules/`. Always-on rules load every session. Path-scoped rules auto-load when matching files are touched. See "Path-scoped rules" below.

`.claude/rules/*.md` is canonical. AGENTS.md is the entry point. It points at the rules and keeps a few load-bearing lines visible without a path trigger, but it does not duplicate rule content. If AGENTS.md and a rule file conflict, the rule file wins.

